# Fuchitron — gitignore

# ─── OS junk ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# ─── Editors ──────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# ─── Adobe / Figma / Sketch sources ───────────────────────
*.ai
*.fig
*.sketch
*.afdesign
*.afphoto
*.psd
*.xd

# ─── Variant / backup / test assets ───────────────────────
# Cualquier archivo con estos sufijos en cualquier carpeta
*-backup.*
*-test.*
*-new.*
*-old.*
*-final.*
*-temp.*
*-tmp.*
*-copy.*
*_backup.*
*_test.*
*_new.*
*_old.*
*_final.*
*_temp.*
*_tmp.*
*_copy.*
*-og.*
*-rendered.*
*-rsng.*
*-t2.*
*-v[0-9].*

# ─── Logs / runtime ───────────────────────────────────────
*.log
*.tmp
*.wav.tmp
backups/
backups/
backups/
node_modules/

# ─── Local-only deploy shim ───────────────────────────────
.vercel/

# ─── Internal notes (kept in workspace only, never in repo) ──
# Si en algún momento movemos docs sensibles a una subcarpeta:
# Fuchitron-private-notes/
# Fuchitron-internal/